<plot>A Kentucky slave (Ossie Davis) fights for his freedom from cruel overseer (Stephen Boyd) whose mistress (Dionne Warwick) eventually joins Davis and the other slaves in their revolt. Co-written and directed by blacklisted Herbert J. Biberman ("Salt of the Earth"). His blacklisted wife Gale Sondergaard's first film in 20 years.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?501125</url></doc>
